      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Classic:

    Play through modes and maps based on games from the Baldi''s
    Basics franchise!

    Field Trips:

    Go on a field trip with Baldi to play
    minigames and try to beat high scores!

    Multiplayer:

    Play as students
    and work together to escape or play as baldi and catch the students!

    Open
    World:

    Explore a large map and complete tasks to progress through a new
    story!


    The greyed out modes are still very unfinished and will be in development
    for a while.

    Sorry about that!'
